org.drip.calc.output

Class BondWorkoutMeasures

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.drip.analytics.core.Serializer
      • org.drip.calc.output.BondWorkoutMeasures

  • public class BondWorkoutMeasures
extends Serializer
    This class encapsulates the parsimonius but complete set of measures generated out of a full bond analytics run to a given work-out.
